text: Kananikolskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kananikolsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 805 as of 2010. There are 40 streets. == Geography == It is located 70 km from Zilair. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Kananikolskoye
